p: Comparing the chemical composition of hydrodistilled of flower- and leaves-derived oil of F. tingitana, α-thujene, α-terpinoline, decanal, fenchyl acetate, elemol, cadinol, and eudesmol were present in both samples in comparable amounts. Carene, ocimene, myecene, and caryophyllene were detected in flower-derived oil not detected in leaves-oil.
